  "text": "Only performance for FAMACHA scores was associated with markers located on OAR3. The two SNPs identified (explaining a total of 10.72 % of the phenotypic variance for this trait) were located in distant chromosomal areas with marker OAR3_161498140.1 located in the relative vicinity of the INFG locus (Table 1 ). This scenario is consistent with expectations suggesting that several OAR3 areas harbor genes with a role in GIN resistance traits [CITATION_1] .",
